    Scope and Contents
McCollum discusses his coal mining experiences in southern Illinois: coal companies, coal production, coal dust and gas, mine ventilation, a visit to mines in Russia, the use of oil versus coal, pit and strip mines, and John L. Lewis and unions. 2 tapes, 180 mins. 
Interview by Barbara Herndon, ca. 1975 
